    "originContent": "You have 2 options for building GCC:",
    "translatedContent": "Vous avez 2 options pour construire GCC :"
  },
  {
    "row": 46,
    "rowsha": "7MbiCql39BSTnR28ZmJqdAmWqjIigKxHmdza3WXxHdA=",
    "originContent": " - `make m68k-toolchain` - Without Newlib",
    "translatedContent": " - `make m68k-toolchain` - Sans Newlib"
  },
  {
    "row": 47,
    "rowsha": "g++39d/XsvZbEFbW0IBgiR+AJ+3XseuRopZv0pxDpOU=",
    "originContent": " - `make m68k-toolchain-newlib` - With Newlib",
    "translatedContent": " - `make m68k-toolchain-newlib` - Avec Newlib"
  },
  {
    "row": 48,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 49,
    "rowsha": "wJHfyHUJYy6+XL9muTpkHxhApEYcYbmd7l5Fvjpe4EE=",
    "originContent": "For 32X, the `sh` toolchain must also be built.",
    "translatedContent": "Pour le 32X, la chaîne d'outils `sh` doit également être construite."
  },
  {
    "row": 50,
    "rowsha": "tpvPUaLsCU/I4CVp5foM+vUwfbc9k49FcUEL2O3QO3c=",
    "originContent": "The options are the same, swapping out `m68k` in the commands above with `sh`.",
    "translatedContent": "Les options sont les mêmes, en remplaçant `m68k` par `sh` dans les commandes ci-dessus."
  },
  {
    "row": 51,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 52,
    "rowsha": "oWopUwbtIS6awDk444K/y2y+kSQVzB7+IATVJ4NFR3k=",
    "originContent": "If you want a different GCC version, or to build specific languages:",
    "translatedContent": "Si vous souhaitez une version différente de GCC, ou construire des langages spécifiques :"
  },
  {
    "row": 53,
    "rowsha": "2fpH30/ZNT/4DtDNgBov7cyoIjtgUwOuXteZCpaoXag=",
    "originContent": " - `make m68k-toolchain-newlib GCC_VER=12.4.0 LANGS=c,c++`",
    "translatedContent": " - `make m68k-toolchain-newlib GCC_VER=12.4.0 LANGS=c,c++`"
  },
  {
    "row": 54,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
