  {
    "row": 68,
    "rowsha": "iAh3rHGMJg3ZBOUns69gayZzDiNfQq2BA7l0ZG3c0ro=",
    "originContent": "OpenJDK needs to be added to the PATH.",
    "translatedContent": "OpenJDK doit être ajouté au PATH."
  },
  {
    "row": 69,
    "rowsha": "5EQ5Zbzyrwywv4lTpDVJCXgrtD62OEh7NhRZVEctKf0=",
    "originContent": " - Open `~/.zshrc` (or `~/.bashrc` if you still use bash) and add the line:",
    "translatedContent": " - Ouvrez `~/.zshrc` (ou `~/.bashrc` si vous utilisez encore bash) et ajoutez la ligne :"
  },
  {
    "row": 70,
    "rowsha": "TJYol0RgMUsKDWvJVpiAGLUqqsN88RBcCH9lu5ydTdI=",
    "originContent": "    - `export PATH=\"/usr/local/opt/openjdk/bin:$PATH\"`",
    "translatedContent": "    - `export PATH=\"/usr/local/opt/openjdk/bin:$PATH\"`"
  },
  {
    "row": 71,
    "rowsha": "3d3lkPwIZnlP0Es6e6HUbjjwMzZqPMFinQul3nkJs/4=",
    "originContent": " - Restart the terminal or run `source ~/.zshrc`",
    "translatedContent": " - Redémarrez le terminal ou exécutez `source ~/.zshrc`"
  },
  {
    "row": 72,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
